item.title: 2021-12-01 17:00 Sundsvall Lounge Hack #284 - Advent of lounge - Sundsvall Lounge Hackers
item.description: It's an open house kind of thing, just bring your computer and show up when you can make time. Some show up earlier, and we'll be here until we get too tired and go home, usually around 11 pm. We'll be sitting in the lounge at the newly built Clarion Hotel Sundsvall thi...
